{"tid":1307779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇法律人? 公識人員行為失當罪, 可唔可以告警察?","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T18:08:41.000Z","uid":263176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0eb1b49b02441d62e638d0856da4cb8776fee6","tid":1307779,"uid":263176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:54:11.000Z","msg":"是針對公職人員各種形式的嚴重濫用職權行為，屬普通法罪行的一種。<br />\n根據終審法院的判例，《公職人員行為失當》罪要滿足以下條件方會成立，包括：<br />\n一）是公職人員；<br />\n二）在擔任公職期間或在與擔任公職有關的情況下；<br />\n三）藉作為或不作為而故意作出不當行為，例如故意忽略或不履行其職責；<br />\n四）沒有合理辯解或理由；<br />\n及五）考慮到有關公職和任職者的責任、<br />\n<br />\n冇Show Pass 明顯中曬. <br />\n如果見到犯打人唔拉又係."},{"pid":"b3f888a2d60bfc9e5cdaf3d185bac5cce847acf3","tid":1307779,"uid":270977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54520d87b7bde0772191ba37135e4435061e6630","tid":1307779,"uid":169154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/press/index_id_521.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress%2Findex_id_521.html&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjtT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=7a221433\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/press/index_id_521.html</a>"},{"pid":"6a33401c7cc69651b496285313807ac37546b35a","tid":1307779,"uid":263176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54520d87b7bde0772191ba37135e4435061e6630","tid":1307779,"uid":169154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/press/index_id_521.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icac.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress%2Findex_id_521.html&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjtT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=7a221433\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icac.org.hk/tc/press/index_id_521.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T18:08:41.000Z","msg":"唔一定收片先入到, <br />\n<br />\n南丫海難為例, <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href